sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_626a25ba37616e0054db43ba54990eb1
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.AlexaUtils</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>AlexaUtils</name><script><![CDATA[var AlexaUtils = Class.create();
AlexaUtils.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	getAuthorizationKeys: function() {
		var output = {};
		output.secretCode = this.getSecretCode();
		output.token = (new AlexaAjaxUtils()).getAlexaAccessToken() + '';
		return JSON.stringify(output);
	},
	
	getSecretCode: function() {
		var tokenFound = true;
		var token, gr;
		var sessionID = gs.getSessionID();
		while(tokenFound) {
			token = Math.floor((Math.random() * 900000) + 1).toFixed(0);
			gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_session');
			gr.addQuery('u_secret_token',token);
			gr.query();
			tokenFound = gr.next();
		}
		gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_session');
		gr.addQuery('u_session_id', sessionID);
		gr.query();
		gs.log('** getSecretCode - session id = ' + sessionID);
		if(gr.next()){
			gr.u_secret_token = token;
		} else {
			gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_session');
			gr.u_session_id = sessionID;
			gr.u_secret_token = token;
		}
		gr.update();
		
		return token.toString();
	},
	
	getPredefinedCodes: function() {
		var code = "1234567890";
		var voiceArry = {};
		voiceArry["wakeup"] = gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.custom.wake")?gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.custom.wake"):gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.wake");
		voiceArry["prefix"] = gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.custom.prefix")?gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.custom.prefix"):gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.prefix");
		for(var i=0; i<code.toString().length; i++) {
			voiceArry[code[i]] = gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.custom." + code[i])?gs.getProperty("alexa.voice.custom" + code[i]):gs.getProperty("alexa.voice." + code[i]);
		}
		return JSON.stringify(voiceArry);
	},
	
	set: function() {
		//gs.log('cs_getProperty:  in the get property script include');
		var prop_name = this.getParameter('sysparm_prop_name');
		var prop_value = this.getParameter('sysparm_prop_value');
		gs.setProperty('temp.prop.'+prop_name, prop_value);
		return 'done';
	},
	saveAudio: function(){
		var propName = this.getParameter('sysparm_prop_name');
		var tempPropValue = gs.getProperty('temp.prop.' +propName);
		gs.setProperty("alexa.voice.custom."+propName, tempPropValue);
		
		return 'done';
		
	},
	getPendingActions: function(){
		var sessions = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_session');
		var currentSessionId = gs.getSessionID();
		sessions.addQuery('u_session_id',currentSessionId);
		sessions.addQuery('u_state','PENDING');
		sessions.setLimit(1);
		sessions.query();
		var pendingAction ;
		while(sessions.next()){
			pendingAction = sessions.u_pending_actions;
			gs.log('pollingjs '+pendingAction);
			sessions.u_state = 'COMPLETE';
			sessions.update();
		}
		return pendingAction.toString();
		
	},
	
	getRegisteredInstances: function() {
		var result = [];
		var item = {};
		var gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
		gr.query();
		while(gr.next()) {
			item = {};
			item.value = gr.u_instance_name + '';
			item.label = gr.u_instance_name + '';
			result.push(item);
		}
		return JSON.stringify(result);
	},
	
	getInstanceName : function(encryptedToken){
		//decrypting user token from alexa
		var decryptedToken ;
		var ge = new GlideEncrypter();
		try{
			decryptedToken =  JSON.parse(ge.decrypt(unescape(decodeURIComponent(encryptedToken))));
		}
		catch(e){
			gs.info('this is decrypted token'+decryptedToken);
		}
		
		return decryptedToken?decryptedToken.instance_name:'';
	},
	
	getUserName : function(encryptedToken){
		//decrypting user token from alexa
		var decryptedToken ;
		var ge = new GlideEncrypter();
		try{
			decryptedToken =  JSON.parse(ge.decrypt(unescape(decodeURIComponent(encryptedToken))));
		}
		catch(e){
			gs.info('this is decrypted token'+decryptedToken);
		}
		
		return decryptedToken?decryptedToken.username:'';
	},
	
	getDecryptedToken : function(encryptedToken){
		//decrypting user token from alexa
		var decryptedToken ;
		var ge = new GlideEncrypter();
		try{
			decryptedToken =  JSON.parse(ge.decrypt(unescape(decodeURIComponent(encryptedToken))));
		}
		catch(e){
			gs.info('this is decrypted token'+decryptedToken);
		}
		gs.info(JSON.stringify(decryptedToken));
		
		return this._getAccessTokenForDecryptedAlexaToken(decryptedToken);
	},
	
	processSessionData : function(session,intentname){
		gs.info('current session'+session);
		gs.info('current intent'+intentname);
		if(session){
			gs.info('session data arrived'+JSON.stringify(session));
			gs.info('current intent'+intentname);
			if(session.next){
				if(session.next.indexOf(intentname) == -1){
					return true;
				}else{
					return false;
				}
			}else{
				return false;
			}
		}
		
	},
	
	authorizeCredentials: function() {
		var ge = new GlideEncrypter();
		var output = {};
		//var instanceName = this.getParameter('sysparm_instance');
		var userObj = this.getParameter('sysparam_object');
		gs.info("userObj: " +JSON.parse(userObj));
		userObj = JSON.parse(userObj);
		gs.info("userObj:"+ userObj.instance);
		//var username = this.getParameter('sysparm_username');
		//var password = this.getParameter('sysparm_password');
		var gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
		gr.addQuery('u_instance_name',userObj.instance);
		gr.query();
		var client_id = '';
		var client_secret = '';
		
		if(gr.next()) {
			client_id = encodeURIComponent(gr.u_client_id);
			var Encrypter = new GlideEncrypter();
			client_secret = encodeURIComponent(Encrypter.decrypt(gr.u_client_secret));
		}
		gs.info("client_id" + client_id);
		var endPoint = 'https://' + userObj.instance + '.service-now.com/oauth_token.do';
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(endPoint);
		var payload = 'client_id=' + client_id + '&client_secret=' + client_secret + '&grant_type=password&username=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.username) + '&password=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.password);
		
		request.addHeader('Content-Type', 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded');
		gs.log('End point = ' + endPoint);
		var response = request.post(payload);
		var result = response.getBody();
		result = JSON.parse(result);
		if(result.error) {
			output.error = result.error;
			output.error_description = result.error_description;
		}else {
			var buildToken = {};
			buildToken.instance_name = userObj.instance;
			buildToken.username = userObj.username;
			buildToken.salt = Math.floor((Math.random() * 9000000) + 1).toFixed(0);
			
			var userSysId = this._fetchTenantUserId(userObj.instance, result.access_token);
			var alexaTenantUserRecord = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenant_userinfo');
			alexaTenantUserRecord.addQuery('u_username',userObj.username);
			alexaTenantUserRecord.addQuery('u_instance_name',userObj.instance);
			alexaTenantUserRecord.query();
			if(alexaTenantUserRecord.next()){
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token = result.access_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_refresh_token = result.refresh_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token_expiry = result.expires_in;
			}else{
				alexaTenantUserRecord.initialize();
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_username = userObj.username;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token = result.access_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_refresh_token = result.refresh_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_instance_name = userObj.instance;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token_expiry = result.expires_in;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_user_sysid = userSysId;
			}
			alexaTenantUserRecord.update();
			output.access_token = encodeURIComponent(escape(ge.encrypt(JSON.stringify(buildToken))));
		}
		gs.log('*** response = ' + JSON.stringify(output));
		return JSON.stringify(output);
	},
	
	_fetchTenantUserId: function(instanceName, accessToken) {
		var userSysId = '';
		// Need to expose a REST API to get the userId.
		var endPoint = 'https://' + instanceName + '.service-now.com/api/snc/alexa_user';
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(endPoint);
		request.addHeader('Authorization', 'Bearer ' + accessToken);
		request.addHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
		var response = request.get();
		var result = JSON.parse(response.getBody());
		if(result) {
			userSysId = result['result']?result['result']['userId']:'';
			gs.log('in _fetchTenantUserId -- user sysid = ' + userSysId);
			
		}
		return userSysId;
	},
	
	_getAccessTokenForDecryptedAlexaToken: function(decryptedToken){
		gs.info(decryptedToken);
		var resultAccessToken = '';
		try {
			
			var instanceName = decryptedToken.instance_name;
			var userName = decryptedToken.username;
			
			var grant_type = 'refresh_token',clientId,clientSecret,refreshToken,output;
			
			var tenantInfo = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
			tenantInfo.addQuery('u_instance_name',instanceName);
			tenantInfo.query();
			
			if(tenantInfo.next()){
				gs.info('Got the tenant info!');
				clientId = tenantInfo.getValue('u_client_id');
				clientSecret = new GlideEncrypter().decrypt(tenantInfo.getValue('u_client_secret'));
			}
			
			var tenantUserInfo = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenant_userinfo');
			tenantUserInfo.addQuery('u_instance_name',instanceName);
			tenantUserInfo.addQuery('u_username',userName);
			tenantUserInfo.query();
			
			if(tenantUserInfo.next()){
				if(!this._isAccessTokenExpired(tenantUserInfo.sys_updated_on, tenantUserInfo.u_access_token_expiry)){
					resultAccessToken = tenantUserInfo.getValue('u_access_token');
				}else {
					refreshToken = tenantUserInfo.getValue('u_refresh_token');
					var oauthResponse = this._getAccessTokenFromRefreshToken(instanceName, clientId, clientSecret, refreshToken);
					resultAccessToken = oauthResponse.access_token;
					tenantUserInfo.u_access_token = resultAccessToken;
					tenantUserInfo.u_access_token_expiry = oauthResponse.expires_in;
					tenantUserInfo.update();
				}
			}
		}catch(ex) {
			gs.info(ex);
		}
		return resultAccessToken;
	},
	
	_isAccessTokenExpired: function(updateDate, expirySeconds) {
		var gDT = new GlideDateTime(updateDate);
		var millisec = gDT.getNumericValue() + (expirySeconds*1000) - 100;
		var currentDateTime = new GlideDateTime(gs.nowNoTZ());
		var millisecNow = currentDateTime.getNumericValue();
		gs.log('is token expired'+(millisecNow > millisec));
		return (millisecNow > millisec);
	},
	
	_getAccessTokenFromRefreshToken: function(instanceName, clientId, clientSecret, refreshToken) {
		gs.info('calling _getAccessTokenFromRefreshToken....');
		var authURL = 'https://' +instanceName+'.service-now.com/oauth_token.do';
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(authURL);
		var payload = 'client_id=' + clientId + '&client_secret=' + clientSecret + '&grant_type=refresh_token' + '&refresh_token='+refreshToken;
		var output = {};
		
		gs.info("acces token fetch payload "+ payload);
		
		request.addHeader('Content-Type', 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded');
		request.addHeader('Accept','application/json');
		gs.info('Payload = ' + payload);
		gs.info('End point = ' + authURL);
		var response = request.post(payload);
		var result = response.getBody();
		result = JSON.parse(result);
		if(result.error) {
			output.error = result.error;
			output.error_description = result.error_description;
			return JSON.stringify(output);
		}else {
			// updating the access token back to the user info table.
			gs.log(result+'access token');
			output.access_token = result.access_token;
			output.expires_in = result.expires_in;
			
		}
		return output;
	},
	
	getCallerInfo: function(isIntegrationUser, accessToken, instanceName, userName, secretCode) {
		gs.log('is Integration user in caller' + isIntegrationUser);
		gs.log('valid accesstoken in caller' + accessToken);
		gs.log('valid username in caller' + userName);
		gs.log('valid secretcode in caller' + secretCode);
		var output = {};
		if(isIntegrationUser) {
			var instanceUrl =  'https://' +instanceName+'.service-now.com/api/snc/alexa_user/'+secretCode;
			var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(instanceUrl);
			request.addHeader("Authorization","Bearer "+accessToken);
			request.addHeader('Accept','application/json');
			var response = request.get();
			var result = response.getBody();
			var userdetails  = JSON.parse(result);
			gs.info('In getCallerInfo -- result = ' + JSON.Stringify(userdetails.result));
			if(result) {
				output.userId = userdetails.result.userId;
				output.userName = userdetails.result.userName;
				gs.info('userdetails from secret code'+output.userId);
			}
		}else {
			var gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenant_userinfo');
			gr.addQuery('u_username', userName);
			gr.addQuery('u_instance_name', instanceName);
			gr.query();
			if(gr.next()){
				output.userId = gr.u_user_sysid + '';
				output.userName = userName;
			}
		}
		return output;
	},
	createIncident : function(instanceName,token,attributes,callerinfo){
		var payload = {};
		payload.caller_id = callerinfo.userId;
		payload.short_description = attributes.short_description;
		payload.urgency = attributes.urgency;
		gs.info('incident payload'+JSON.stringify(payload));
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest
		('https://'+instanceName+'.service-now.com/api/now/table/incident');
		request.addHeader("Authorization","Bearer "+token);
		request.addHeader('Accept','application/json');
		request.addHeader('Content-Type','application/json');
		var response = request.post(JSON.stringify(payload));
		gs.log(response.getStatusCode());
		gs.log(response.getBody());
		var data = response.getBody();
		var output = JSON.parse(data);
		attributes.sys_id = output.result.sys_id;
		return output.result.number;
		
	},
	getOppurtunities : function(instanceName,token,attributes,callerinfo,accountname){
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest
		('https://'+instanceName+'.service-now.com/api/17295/oppurtunities?account='+accountname);
		request.addHeader("Authorization","Bearer "+token);
		request.addHeader('Accept','application/json');
		request.addHeader('Content-Type','application/json');
		var response = request.get();
		gs.log(response.getStatusCode());
		gs.log(response.getBody());
		var data = response.getBody();
		var output = JSON.parse(data);
		return output.result;
		
	},
	updatePendingaction :function(instaneName,token,attributes,secretcode){
		var inputdata = {};
		var action = {};
		action.type = 'redirect';
		action.data = 'http://'+instaneName+'service-now.com/nav_to.do?uri=sys_script_include.do?sys_id='+attributes.sys_id;
		inputdata.payload = action;
		inputdata.secretcode = attributes.secretcode;
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest
		('https://'+instanceName+'.service-now.com/api/x_snc_amazon_echo/pendingaction');
		request.addHeader("Authorization","Bearer "+token);
		request.addHeader('Accept','application/json');
		request.addHeader('Content-Type','application/json');
		var response = request.post(JSON.stringify(inputdata));
		gs.log(response.getStatusCode());
		gs.log(response.getBody());
		var data = response.getBody();
		gs.info("pending action processed"+data);
		
	},
	passOnVoiceRequest: function(instanceUrl,accessToken,requestBody){
		var requestToTargetInstance = new GlideHTTPRequest(instanceUrl);
		requestToTargetInstance.addHeader("Authorization","Bearer "+accessToken);
		requestToTargetInstance.addHeader('Accept','application/json');
		requestToTargetInstance.addHeader('Content-Type','application/json');
// 		requestToTargetInstance.payload=JSON.stringify(requestBody);
		
		var responseFromTargetInstance = requestToTargetInstance.post(JSON.stringify(requestBody));
		var result = responseFromTargetInstance.getBody();
		var httpStatus = responseFromTargetInstance.getStatusCode();
		var voiceOutput  = JSON.parse(result);
		gs.info('voiceOutput = ' + JSON.Stringify(voiceOutput));
		return voiceOutput;
		
	},
	type: 'AlexaUtils'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>admin</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-02 20:16:04</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>626a25ba37616e0054db43ba54990eb1</sys_id><sys_mod_count>130</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AlexaUtils</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_626a25ba37616e0054db43ba54990eb1</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>anil.akula</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-26 08:38:59</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

	gs.info('*** intent LauchRequest called...');
	erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Welcome to the ServiceNow Alexa app. What can I help you with? For a list of commands, say 'Help'.");
	erb.setReprompt("PlainText", "How can I help you?");
	erb.setEnd(false);

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_email"><sys_script_email action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>alexa.email.notificationscript</name><new_lines_to_html>false</new_lines_to_html><script><![CDATA[(function runMailScript(current, template, email, email_action, event) {
	
	//gs.info("alexa " + JSON.stringify(event.p));
	var parsed = new global.JSON().decode(event.parm2);
	gs.info("parsed " + parsed);
	if(parsed == undefined || parsed == null)
		parsed = {};
	var name = parsed.fromName +" <"+parsed.fromEmail+">";
	/*parsed.subject = "Alexa - ServiceNow Integration";
	parsed.body = "Hello Alexa. Welcome to servicenow application ";*/
	if(parsed.formName == "")
		name = parsed.fromEmail;
	gs.info("alexa name "+ name);
	gs.info("alexa body "+ parsed.body);
	gs.info("alexa  subject " + parsed.subject);
	template.print(parsed.body);
	gs.info("after temaplte print statment ");
	email.setFrom(name);
	email.setSubject(parsed.subject);
	
	
})(current, template, email, email_action, event);]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_email</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>karunakar.medamoni</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-10-19 10:29:13</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>60f665b1dba622804a54f4bbaf9619e7</sys_id><sys_mod_count>11</sys_mod_count><sys_name>alexa.email.notificationscript</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_email_60f665b1dba622804a54f4bbaf9619e7</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Karunakar.m</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-10-20 12:27:50</sys_updated_on></sys_script_email></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance_ced2f935db86e200c2f3717bbf96191f
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><keyword>NumberIntent</keyword><name>NumberIntent</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	var alexaUtils = new global.AlexaUtils();
	if(attributes && content.number && content.number.value){
		attributes.number = content.number.value;
		if(attributes.transaction == 'UserLink') {
			// link your secret code to the user id in the tenant instance.
			var secretCode = content.number.value;
			gs.info('IN number intent --> ' + isIntegrationUser + '::' + token + '::' + instanceName + '::' + userName + '::' + secretCode);
			var callerInfo = alexaUtils.getCallerInfo(isIntegrationUser, token, instanceName, userName, secretCode);
			if(callerInfo && callerInfo.userId){
				attributes.snow_user_id = callerInfo.userId;
				attributes.transaction = '';
				attributes.next = undefined;
			}
			erb.setAttributes(attributes);
			erb.setEnd(false);
						
		}else if(attributes.transaction == 'PriorityNumber'){
			var caller_info = {'userName': userName, 'userId': attributes.snow_user_id};
			if(attributes && attributes.short_description && content.number && content.number.value){
				attributes.urgency = content.number.value;				
				var incidentNumber = alexaUtils.createIncident(instanceName,token,attributes,caller_info);
				if(incidentNumber){
					erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Your incident was logged successfully ,here is your incident number "+incidentNumber.split('').join(' '),"");
				}else{
					erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "I am sorry ,i got confused can you please try after sometime, or else yoy can try one more time by saying my problem is, your problem statment","");
				}
				gs.info('in callerinfo priority'+JSON.stringify(caller_info));
				erb.setAttributes(attributes);
				erb.setEnd(true);
			}else{
				if(!attributes.short_description){
					attributes.next = 'DescriptionIntent';
					erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "You cant say your urgency before your problem is known , please let me know your problem by saying my problem is .., your problem statement","");
					erb.setAttributes(attributes);
					erb.setEnd(false);
				}else{
					erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Sorry i missed your urgency level ,can you please rate your level of urgency on a scale of one to three where one is most priority and three is least","");
					erb.setAttributes(attributes);
					erb.setEnd(false);
				}
			}
						
		}else{
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Hello, got the number");
			erb.setAttributes(attributes);
			erb.setEnd(false);
		}
		
	}
	result = erb.getResponse();
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>chaitanya.s</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-24 14:48:14</sys_created_on><sys_id>ced2f935db86e200c2f3717bbf96191f</sys_id><sys_mod_count>15</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>chaitanya.s</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-27 10:35:45</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.VoicePortalUtil</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>VoicePortalUtil</name><script><![CDATA[var VoicePortalUtil = Class.create();
VoicePortalUtil.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
	getRegisteredInstances: function() {
		var result = [];
		var item = {};
		var gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
		gr.query();
		while(gr.next()) {
			item = {};
			item.value = gr.u_instance_name + '';
			item.label = gr.u_instance_name + '';
			result.push(item);
		}
		return JSON.stringify(result);
	},
	
	authorizeCredentials: function() {
		var ge = new GlideEncrypter();
		var output = {};
		//var instanceName = this.getParameter('sysparm_instance');
		var userObj = this.getParameter('sysparam_object');
		gs.info("userObj: " +JSON.parse(userObj));
		userObj = JSON.parse(userObj);
		gs.info("userObj:"+ userObj.instance);
		//var username = this.getParameter('sysparm_username');
		//var password = this.getParameter('sysparm_password');
		var gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
		gr.addQuery('u_instance_name',userObj.instance);
		gr.query();
		var client_id = '';
		var client_secret = '';
		
		if(gr.next()) {
			client_id = encodeURIComponent(gr.u_client_id);
			var Encrypter = new GlideEncrypter();
			client_secret = encodeURIComponent(Encrypter.decrypt(gr.u_client_secret));
		}
		gs.info("client_id" + client_id);
		var endPoint = 'https://' + userObj.instance + '.service-now.com/oauth_token.do';
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(endPoint);
		var payload = 'client_id=' + client_id + '&client_secret=' + client_secret + '&grant_type=password&username=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.username) + '&password=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.password);
		
		request.addHeader('Content-Type', 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded');
		gs.log('End point = ' + endPoint);
		var response = request.post(payload);
		var result = response.getBody();
		result = JSON.parse(result);
		if(result.error) {
			output.error = result.error;
			output.error_description = result.error_description;
		}else {
			var buildToken = {};
			buildToken.instance_name = userObj.instance;
			buildToken.username = userObj.username;
			buildToken.salt = Math.floor((Math.random() * 9000000) + 1).toFixed(0);
			
			var userSysId = this._fetchTenantUserId(userObj.instance, result.access_token);
			var alexaTenantUserRecord = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenant_userinfo');
			alexaTenantUserRecord.addQuery('u_username',userObj.username);
			alexaTenantUserRecord.addQuery('u_instance_name',userObj.instance);
			alexaTenantUserRecord.query();
			if(alexaTenantUserRecord.next()){
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token = result.access_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_refresh_token = result.refresh_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token_expiry = result.expires_in;
			}else{
				alexaTenantUserRecord.initialize();
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_username = userObj.username;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token = result.access_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_refresh_token = result.refresh_token;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_instance_name = userObj.instance;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_access_token_expiry = result.expires_in;
				alexaTenantUserRecord.u_user_sysid = userSysId;
			}
			alexaTenantUserRecord.update();
			output.access_token = encodeURIComponent(escape(ge.encrypt(JSON.stringify(buildToken))));
		}
		gs.log('*** response = ' + JSON.stringify(output));
		return JSON.stringify(output);
	},
	
	_fetchTenantUserId: function(instanceName, accessToken) {
		var userSysId = '';
		// Need to expose a REST API to get the userId.
		var endPoint = 'https://' + instanceName + '.service-now.com/api/snc/alexa_user';
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(endPoint);
		request.addHeader('Authorization', 'Bearer ' + accessToken);
		request.addHeader('Content-Type', 'application/json');
		var response = request.get();
		var result = JSON.parse(response.getBody());
		if(result) {
			userSysId = result['result']?result['result']['userId']:'';
			gs.log('in _fetchTenantUserId -- user sysid = ' + userSysId);
			
		}
		return userSysId;
	},
	
	_getAccessTokenForDecryptedAlexaToken: function(decryptedToken){
		gs.info(decryptedToken);
		var resultAccessToken = '';
		try {
			
			var instanceName = decryptedToken.instance_name;
			var userName = decryptedToken.username;
			
			var grant_type = 'refresh_token',clientId,clientSecret,refreshToken,output;
			
			var tenantInfo = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
			tenantInfo.addQuery('u_instance_name',instanceName);
			tenantInfo.query();
			
			if(tenantInfo.next()){
				gs.info('Got the tenant info!');
				clientId = tenantInfo.getValue('u_client_id');
				clientSecret = new GlideEncrypter().decrypt(tenantInfo.getValue('u_client_secret'));
			}
			
			var tenantUserInfo = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenant_userinfo');
			tenantUserInfo.addQuery('u_instance_name',instanceName);
			tenantUserInfo.addQuery('u_username',userName);
			tenantUserInfo.query();
			
			if(tenantUserInfo.next()){
				if(!this._isAccessTokenExpired(tenantUserInfo.sys_updated_on, tenantUserInfo.u_access_token_expiry)){
					resultAccessToken = tenantUserInfo.getValue('u_access_token');
				}else {
					refreshToken = tenantUserInfo.getValue('u_refresh_token');
					var oauthResponse = this._getAccessTokenFromRefreshToken(instanceName, clientId, clientSecret, refreshToken);
					resultAccessToken = oauthResponse.access_token;
					tenantUserInfo.u_access_token = resultAccessToken;
					tenantUserInfo.u_access_token_expiry = oauthResponse.expires_in;
					tenantUserInfo.update();
				}
			}
		}catch(ex) {
			gs.info(ex);
		}
		return resultAccessToken;
	},
	
	_isAccessTokenExpired: function(updateDate, expirySeconds) {
		var gDT = new GlideDateTime(updateDate);
		var millisec = gDT.getNumericValue() + (expirySeconds*1000) - 5000;
		var currentDateTime = new GlideDateTime(gs.nowNoTZ());
		var millisecNow = currentDateTime.getNumericValue();
		gs.log('is token expired'+(millisecNow > millisec));
		return (millisecNow > millisec);
	},
	
	_getAccessTokenFromRefreshToken: function(instanceName, clientId, clientSecret, refreshToken) {
		gs.info('calling _getAccessTokenFromRefreshToken....');
		var authURL = 'https://' +instanceName+'.service-now.com/oauth_token.do';
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(authURL);
		var payload = 'client_id=' + clientId + '&client_secret=' + clientSecret + '&grant_type=refresh_token' + '&refresh_token='+refreshToken;
		var output = {};
		
		gs.info("acces token fetch payload "+ payload);
		
		request.addHeader('Content-Type', 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded');
		request.addHeader('Accept','application/json');
		gs.info('Payload = ' + payload);
		gs.info('End point = ' + authURL);
		var response = request.post(payload);
		var result = response.getBody();
		result = JSON.parse(result);
		if(result.error) {
			output.error = result.error;
			output.error_description = result.error_description;
			return JSON.stringify(output);
		}else {
			// updating the access token back to the user info table.
			gs.log(result+'access token');
			output.access_token = result.access_token;
			output.expires_in = result.expires_in;
			
		}
		return output;
	},
	
	isPublic: function(){
		return true;
	},
	
	type: 'VoicePortalUtil'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>chaitanya.s</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-10-19 09:01:28</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>c6331df9db2eaa00c2f3717bbf96191b</sys_id><sys_mod_count>3</sys_mod_count><sys_name>VoicePortalUtil</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_c6331df9db2eaa00c2f3717bbf96191b</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>chaitanya.s</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-10-19 13:40:16</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><keyword>IncidentPredict</keyword><name>alexaIncidentPredict</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	var responseText = "";
	var number = "";
	
	gs.info("alexa12");
	
	try {
		gs.info("alexa Karunakar");
		var r = new sn_ws.RESTMessageV2('global.alexa_sla_predict', 'get');
		var response = r.execute();
		var responseBody = response.getBody();
		var httpStatus = response.getStatusCode();
		gs.info(responseBody);
		result = global.JSON.parse(responseBody);
		gs.info(result);
		if(result != undefined && result.PredictionList != undefined ){
			/*gs.info("result not undefined ");
			gs.info("  length  of result "+ result.PredictionList.length);
			gs.info(global.JSON.stringify(result.PredictionList)); */
			
			responseText = "Yes , There are " + result.PredictionList.length ;
			// getting incident number 
			
			/*for(var i =0; i < result.PredictionList.length ; i++){
				 number +=  "," +result.PredictionList[i].IncidentNumber;
			}
			responseText += "Incident numbers are " + number;*/
			
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", responseText, "");
			erb.setEnd(false);
			result = erb.getResponse();
			
			
		}else{
			responseText = "There is no incidents found with the request.. Please try with different one ";
			
		}
		
		
	}
	catch(ex) {
		var message = ex.getMessage();
		gs.info(message);
		result = "There is no incidents found with the request.. Please try with different one ";
	}
	
	//gs.info("alexa " +result);
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>Karunakar.m</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-10-19 06:50:48</sys_created_on><sys_id>3a82f8b1db2eaa00c2f3717bbf961908</sys_id><sys_mod_count>27</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>Karunakar.m</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-10-19 09:50:02</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><keyword>PositiveVerb</keyword><name>PositiveVerb</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	if(attributes && attributes.short_description){
		attributes.next = 'PriorityIntent';
		erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Alright !! ,Please rate your urgency on scale of one to three ,where one is most urgent and three is least urgent","");
		erb.setReprompt("PlainText", "I couldnot get that please say one  or two or three", "");
		erb.setAttributes(attributes);
		erb.setEnd(false);
	}
	result = erb.getResponse();
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>anil.akula</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-20 12:00:44</sys_created_on><sys_id>baf5e4e4db42a200c2f3717bbf9619d6</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>anil.akula</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-20 12:00:44</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="content_css"><content_css action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><name>snow-branding</name><style>/* Font and box size overriding for Fuji */
@font-face {
  font-family:"retina_icons";
  src:url("/styles/retina_icons/retina_icons-8208ad73fd96c671803ed3991a2765d3.eot");
  font-weight:normal;
  font-style:normal;
}
@font-face {
  font-family:"retina_icons";
  src:url("/styles/retina_icons/retina_icons-8208ad73fd96c671803ed3991a2765d3.eot");
  src:url("/styles/retina_icons/retina_icons-8208ad73fd96c671803ed3991a2765d3.eot?#iefix") format("embedded-opentype"),
  url("/styles/retina_icons/retina_icons-8208ad73fd96c671803ed3991a2765d3.woff") format("woff"),
  url("/styles/retina_icons/retina_icons-8208ad73fd96c671803ed3991a2765d3.ttf") format("truetype"),
  url("/styles/retina_icons/retina_icons-8208ad73fd96c671803ed3991a2765d3.svg?#retina_icons") format("svg");
  font-weight:normal;
  font-style:normal;
}
* {
  -webkit-box-sizing: initial; 
  -moz-box-sizing: initial;
   
  box-sizing: initial; 
}
/* Font and box size overriding for Fuji end */

/* Body padding and wrapper for sticky footer */
HTML[data-doctype=true] body[data-formName="ui_page_render"] {
  padding: 0px 0px 120px;
}
div.wrapper {
  min-height: 100%;
}
HTML[data-doctype="true"] body.firefox {
  padding: 0px 0px 100px;
}
HTML[data-doctype="true"] body.msie9 {
  padding: 0px 0px 100px;
}
HTML[data-doctype="true"] body.msie10 {
  padding: 0px 0px 100px;
}
HTML[data-doctype="true"] body.msie11 {
  padding: 0px 0px 100px;
}
/* Body padding and wrapper for sticky footer end*/

/* Regular styles */
body {
  margin: 0px !important;
  width: 100%;
  position: relative;
  font-size: 10pt;
}
div#main_header {
  width: 100%;
  height: 77px;
  background-color: #000000;
  padding: 10px 0px;
  box-shadow: 0 10px 6px -6px #999;
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}
div.header-row {
  width: 90%;
  margin: 20px auto 0 auto;
}
#logo {
  width: 208px;
  height: 29px;
  display: block;
  background: url("sso-servicenow-logo-transparent.png") no-repeat;
  text-indent: -1000px;
  -webkit-background-size: contain;
  -moz-background-size: contain;
  -o-background-size: contain;
  background-size: contain;
}
h1.headingText {
  font-family: omnes, 'Gotham Book', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: #646464;
  width: auto;
  position: relative;
  font-size: 2em;
  margin-top: 0.7em;
  margin-bottom: 0.75em;
}
h1.infoText {
  font-family: omnes, 'Gotham Book', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
  height:33px;
  font-weight: 200;
  height: 33px;
  color: #646464;
  width: auto;
  position: relative;
}
div.spacerNum {
  height: 90px;
  width: auto;
}
div.separatorDiv {
  clear: both;
  padding: 2px 0px 1px 0px;
}
div.mainContainer {
  width: 90%;
  margin: 20px auto 0px auto;
  height: auto;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
div.mainContainer div.colLeft {
  width: auto;
  float: left;
  padding: 0px 30px 50px 0px;
  max-width: 525px;
}
div.mainContainer div.colLeft.rgtBdr {
  border-right: 1px solid #dddddd;
}
div.mainContainer div.colRight{
  max-width:475px;
  width: auto;
  float: left;
  padding: 0px 0px 50px 30px;
}
div.mainContainer div.singleCol {
  float: none;
}
/* input[type=text],
input[type=password]{
  width: 300px; 
  font-size: 16px;
  border: 1px solid #e6e8ea;
  padding: 3px 4px 4px;
  box-sizing: border-box;
  margin-left: 3px;
} */
input#submitButton,
input#loginButton,
input#registerButton {
  background-color: #d1232b;
  color: #ffffff;
  border: 1px solid #d1232b;
  border-radius: 5px;
  width: auto;
  padding: 3px 50px;
  margin-left: 3px;
  font-size: 16px;
  cursor: pointer;
  -webkit-appearance: none;
}
div#ssoFooter {
  width: 100%;
  border-top: 1px solid #ddd;
  padding: 10px 0px;
  background-color: #000000;
  bottom: 0;
}
div#ssoFooter div.footerBlock {
  width: 90%;
  height: auto;
  margin: auto;
  font-size: 12px;
  font-weight: 100;
  color: #FFFFFF;
}
div#ssoFooter div.footerBlock ul {
  margin: 0px;
  padding: 0px;
}
div#ssoFooter div.footerBlock ul li{
  display: inline-block;
  border-left: none;
  border-right: 1px solid #FFFFFF;
  margin: 0px 12px 0px 0px;
  padding-right: 12px;
}
div#ssoFooter div.footerBlock ul li a {
  color: #FFFFFF;
}
div#ssoFooter div.footerBlock ul li.lastItem {
  border-right: none;
}
div#browserMessage {
  margin-top: 10px;
}
p {
  display: block;
  -webkit-margin-before: 1em;
  -webkit-margin-after: 1em;
  -webkit-margin-start: 0px;
  -webkit-margin-end: 0px;
}
div#passwordMessagePlaceholderDiv {
  padding-left: 5px;
  font-size: 11px;
  color: rgba(128, 128, 128, 0.66);
  width: 300px;
}
img#refreshCaptchaImage {
  height: 20px;
  width: 20px;
  padding-left: 60px;
}
div#page_timing_div {
  display: none;
}
div.text_caption {
  font-size: 13px;
  color: #646464;
  font-weight: bold;
  text-align: left;
}
p.lgnText {
  color: #333333;
  font-size: 13px;
  margin: 5px 0px 0px 3px;
  text-align: left;
  -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
}
p.lgnText a {
  padding: 3px 6px;
  color: #d1232b;
}
/* Regular styles end */

/* Two column responsive shift */
@media (max-width: 1155px) {
 div.mainContainer div.colLeft,
 div.mainContainer div.colRight { 
    border-right: 0px;
    padding-left: 0px;
  }
  div.mainContainer div.colLeft.rgtBdr {
    border-right: 0px;
  }
}
input#termsOfUse {
  margin: 3px 5px 5px 3px;
}
/* Two column responsive shift end */

/* Styles for Error Messages */
div.showMessage {
color: #3333333;
width: 80%;
border: 1px solid #E6E8EA;
padding: 0px;
border-radius: 3px;
background: #F8F9FA;
margin: 10px 10px;
position: relative;
padding: 10px 15px 15px 5px;
}

div.showMessage span.image-browse-icon.info {
color: #646464;
}

div.showMessage span.image-browse-icon {
font-size: 2em;
display: inline-block;
position: absolute;
top: 0;
margin-left: .1em;
margin-top: .1em;
}

div.showMessage span.image-browse-icon.error {
color: #ff0000;
}
div.showMessage span.infoText {
font-size: 14px;
color: #646464;
font-family: Arial;
display: inline-block;
margin-left: 2.5em;
padding-top: 0.2em;
}  

div#errorPlaceholder a {
color: #D1232B;
} 
/* Styles for Error Messages end */

/* Password Strength */
#pwd_info {
    width: 300px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    box-shadow: 0 1px 3px #ccc;
    border: 1px solid #ddd;
    background: #fefefe;
    padding-right: 2em;
    margin: 0px 0px 10px 3px;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

#pwd_info::before{
  content: "\25B2";
  position:relative;
  left:50%;
}

.valid {
  background:url(/sso-correct-icon.pngx) no-repeat;
  padding-left:20px;
  background-size:15px;
  color:#3a7d34;
}
.invalid {
  background:url(/sso-wrong-icon.pngx) no-repeat;
  padding-left:20px;
  background-size:15px;
  color:#d1232b;
}
/* Password Strength end */

/* IE9.0 quirks */
.ieElement { display: none; }
body.msie9 div.body-vertical-spacer,
body.msie9 div.spacerNum { display: none; }
body.msie9 div#main_header {border-bottom: 1px solid #bbbbbb;}
body.msie9 div.ieElement { display: block; padding-left: 3px; }
body.msie9 img#refreshCaptchaImage {
    margin-left: 35px;
    padding-left: 15px;
    padding-right: 0px;
    height: 20px;
    width: 30px;
  }
body.msie9 div#ssoFooter { margin: 10px 0px 0px; padding: 10px 0px 0px; float: left; }
body.msie9 div#ssoFooter div.footerBlock ul li { float: left; display: block; }
body.msie9 div#ssoFooter div.footerBlock ul li.lastItem {border-right: none;}
body.msie9 div#browserMessage { clear: both; padding-top: 10px}
body.msie9 div.mainContainer div.colLeft { padding-left: 0px;}
body.msie9 div.mainContainer div.colRight,
body.msie9 div.mainContainer div.colLeft {
  float: left !important;
}
/* IE9.0 quirks end */

@media (max-device-width : 480px) {
  body {
    margin: 0px !important;

    max-width:100%;

  input[type=text],

    /*
    font-size: 3em;

    */    
  }

    /*padding: 0.625em 0px;*/

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><keyword>IncidentByGroup</keyword><name>Incidents By Group</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	if(attributes.snow_user_id){
		
		var alexaUtils = new global.AlexaUtils();
		gs.info('*** in incidentsByGroup intent = ' + content.priority);
		var incidents = alexaUtils.fetchIncidentsByUserGroup(instanceName,token,attributes, content.priority);
		if(incidents && incidents.length > 0) {
			incidents = incidents[0];
		}
		if(incidents){	
			gs.info('*** Incidents By Group 1  --> ' + incidents);
			var description = 'Wifi connection';
			if(incidents['description']){
				description = incidents['description'];
				gs.info('*** Incidents By Group --> ' + description);
			}
			var location = 'Hyderabad Office';
			if(incidents['location.name']) {
				location = incidents['location.name'];
			}
			var phone = '+16692623494';		
			if(attributes.userphone) {
				phone = attributes.userphone;
			}
			
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Yes there is one P2 issue about " + description + " that is reported at " + location + ", sending details to your email.");
			attributes.sendemail = true;	
			gs.info(" to email address  "+ attributes.useremail);
			var email = new global.alexaEmailNotification();
			gs.info('callingemail'+global.JSON.stringify(attributes.incidentIds));
			email.sendEmail(attributes.incidentIds,attributes.useremail);
			gs.info('calling after email'+global.JSON.stringify(attributes.incidentIds));
		}else{
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Nothing assigned to your group","");
		}
		
		erb.setAttributes(attributes);
		erb.setEnd(false);
		
		var output = "";
	}else{
		erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Sorry ,i lost your information ,can you please re-authenticate, yourself by saying your launch phrase again");
		erb.setAttributes(attributes);
		erb.setEnd(true);
	}
	result = erb.getResponse();
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>chaitanya.s</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-10-19 15:25:53</sys_created_on><sys_id>d41b6a71db26a600fc3b7ffdbf9619e5</sys_id><sys_mod_count>18</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>chaitanya.s</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-10-22 01:08:40</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: sys_script_include_d9b69212db4ee200fc3b7ffdbf961961
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>public</access><active>true</active><api_name>global.AlexaRegistrationUtil</api_name><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>AlexaRegistrationUtil</name><script><![CDATA[var AlexaRegistrationUtil = Class.create();
AlexaRegistrationUtil.prototype = Object.extendsObject(AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	
	validateUser : function(){
		
		var ge = new GlideEncrypter();
		var output = {};
		var userObj = this.getParameter('sysparam_object');
		gs.info("UserObj 1111"+ userObj);
		userObj = JSON.parse(userObj);
		gs.info("UserObj "+ userObj);
		/* var gr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
		{"email":"karunakar@gmail.com","userid":"karunakar","password":"kannaiah","repassword":"kannaiah","instance_name":"voiceportal.servicenow.com","oauthid":"a;skfasdkf;slkfdak","oauthsecret":"as;dlkfa;lsdkfja;lksdf","tusername":"asdfasdfasdf","tpassword":"asdfasdfasdf"}
		
 		*/
		
		gs.info("UserObj "+ userObj.instance_name);
		
		var endPoint = 'https://' + userObj.instance_name + '.service-now.com/oauth_token.do';
		
		var request = new GlideHTTPRequest(endPoint);
		
		var payload = 'client_id=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.oauthid) + '&client_secret=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.oauthsecret) + '&grant_type=password&username=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.tusername) + '&password=' + encodeURIComponent(userObj.tpassword);
		
		var result = "";
		
		try{
			gs.info('voice portal - payload '+ payload);
			request.addHeader('Content-Type', 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded');
			gs.log('End point = ' + endPoint);
			var response = request.post(payload);
			
			result = response.getBody();
			gs.info('voice portal - payload '+ payload);
			gs.info('voice portal - result '+ result);
			result = JSON.parse(result);
		}catch(error){
			gs.info(" voice portal " + error);
		}
		gs.info('voice portal - result '+ result);
		if(result.error) {
			output.error = result.error;
			output.error_description = result.error_description;
		}else {
			
			
			try{
				
				// tent user_info
				
				var grr = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenant_userinfo');
				grr.addQuery('u_username',userObj.tusername);
				grr.query();
				if(grr.next()){
					output.description += " Tent information is existed .. Please contract system adminstrator";
				}else{
					
					grr.initialize();
					grr.u_is_integration_user = true;
					grr.u_access_token = result.access_token;
					grr.u_instance_name = userObj.instance_name;
					grr.u_refresh_token = result.refresh_token;
					grr.u_username = userObj.tusername;
					
					grr.update();
					
				}
				
				// storing oauth details...
				
				var gr1 = new GlideRecord('u_alexa_tenants');
				gr1.addQuery('u_client_id',userObj.oauthid);
				gr1.query();
				if(gr1.next()){
					
					output.description += " oauth details are existed .. Please contract system adminstrator ";
					
				}else{
					gr1.initialize();
					gr1.u_instance_name = userObj.instance_name;
					gr1.u_client_id = userObj.oauthid;
					gr1.u_client_secret = userObj.oauthsecret;
					
					gr1.update();
					
				}
				
				// storing sys_users
				
				var gr = new GlideRecord('sys_user');
				gr.addQuery('user_name',userObj.userid);
				gr.query();
				if(gr.next()){
					gr.first_name = userObj.userid;
					gr.last_name = userObj.userid;
					output.description += " User already existed .. Please contact system adminstrator ... ";
					
				}else{
					
					gr.initialize();
					gr.user_name = userObj.userid;
					gr.email = userObj.email;
					gr.first_name = userObj.userid;
					gr.last_name = userObj.userid;
					gr.user_password = userObj.password;
					
					gr.update();
				}
			}catch(error){
				output.error_description = " Unable to create user with provided information... Please contact system adminstrator ... ";
			}
		}
		gs.log('*** response = ' + JSON.stringify(output));
		return JSON.stringify(output);
		
	},
	
	
	type: 'AlexaRegistrationUtil'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>Karunakar.m</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-26 06:42:48</sys_created_on><sys_customer_update>true</sys_customer_update><sys_id>d9b69212db4ee200fc3b7ffdbf961961</sys_id><sys_mod_count>15</sys_mod_count><sys_name>AlexaRegistrationUtil</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Global" source="global">global</sys_package><sys_policy/><sys_replace_on_upgrade>false</sys_replace_on_upgrade><sys_scope display_value="Global">global</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_d9b69212db4ee200fc3b7ffdbf961961</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>Karunakar.m</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-26 10:49:17</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>

<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><keyword>DescriptionIntent</keyword><name>DescriptionIntent</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	if(attributes && content.statement && content.statement.value){
		if(attributes.incidentevent){
			attributes.next = 'PriorityIntent';
			attributes.short_description = content.statement.value;
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Please rate your urgency on scale of one to three ,where one is most urgent and three is least urgent","");
			erb.setReprompt("PlainText", "I couldnot get that please say one  or two or three", "");
			erb.setAttributes(attributes);
			erb.setEnd(false);
		}else{
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Do you want me to create an incident ,please say 'yes' to confirm ..,you can say no to cancel ","");
			erb.setReprompt("PlainText", "you can say yes or no", "");
			attributes.next = 'PositiveVerb';
			attributes.short_description = content.statement.value;
			erb.setAttributes(attributes);
			erb.setEnd(false);
		}
	}else{
		erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Sorry i missed your problem statement , can you repeat it by saying, my problem is followed by your problem statement","");
		erb.setReprompt("PlainText", "I couldnot get that please say one  or two or three", "");
		erb.setAttributes(attributes);
		erb.setEnd(false);
		
	}
	result = erb.getResponse();
	
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>anil.akula</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-20 12:03:06</sys_created_on><sys_id>3b86a8e4db42a200c2f3717bbf96192e</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>anil.akula</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-20 12:03:06</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

	var oppurtunities, paginatedOppurtunities, alexaUtils;
	var prefix = '';
	var isFirst,isLastList;
	var responseText = '';
	var result;
	if(attributes.oppurtunities && attributes.currentIndex){
			if((attributes.currentIndex+3) < attributes.oppurtunities.length){
				paginatedOppurtunities = oppurtunities.slice(attributes.currentIndex,attributes.currentIndex+3);
				attributes.currentIndex = attributes.currentIndex+3;
				attributes.next = 'ContinueIntent,RepeatIntent';
				responseText = paginatedOppurtunities.join(',');
				responseText += ',you can say .continue.for next set of list,or cancel for new query ';
			}else{
				paginatedOppurtunities = oppurtunities.slice(attributes.currentIndex,attributes.oppurtunities.length);
				attributes.next = 'RepeatIntent';
				responseText = paginatedOppurtunities.join(',');
				responseText += ',There are no more oppurtunities left to be listed, you can say ,repeat ,to repeat this list again or cancel ';
			}
		attributes.repeat = paginatedOppurtunities;
		erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", responseText, "");
		erb.setReprompt("PlainText", "you can say next or continue or cancel", "");
		erb.setAttributes(attributes);
		erb.setEnd(false);
		result = erb.getResponse();
	}
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>chaitanya.s</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-10-19 06:35:16</sys_created_on><sys_id>90c1b8b1db2eaa00c2f3717bbf9619dd</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>chaitanya.s</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-10-19 06:35:16</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

sys_update_xml.name: x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance_c1281b3ddbc6e200c2f3717bbf961940
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>false</active><keyword>GetOppurtunities</keyword><name>GetOppurtunities</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	
	var oppurtunities, paginatedOppurtunities, alexaUtils;
	var prefix = '';
	var isFirst,isLastList;
	var responseText = '';
	var result;
	if(content.account.value){
			alexaUtils = new AlexaUtils();
			oppurtunities = alexaUtils.getOppurtunities(instanceName,token,attributes,caller_info,content.account.value);
			if(oppurtunities && oppurtunities.length>0){
				attributes.oppurtunities = oppurtunities;
				prefix = 'There are total ,'+ oppurtunities.length +'oppurtunities Identified for '+content.account.value+', Here is your list in chronological order of there modification date. ';
				isFirst = true;
				if(oppurtunities.length >3){
					paginatedOppurtunities = oppurtunities.slice(0,3);
					attributes.currentIndex = 3;
					isLastList = false;
					attributes.next = 'ContinueIntent,RepeatIntent';
					responseText = prefix+paginatedOppurtunities.join(',')+'you can say continue for next set of list or ,repeat , for repeating current set or cancel for cancelling this query';	
				}else{
					paginatedOppurtunities = oppurtunities.slice(0,oppurtunities.length);
					isLastList = true;
					attributes.next = 'RepeatIntent';
					responseText = prefix+paginatedOppurtunities.join(',')+'you can say, repeat ,for repeating current list ';
				}
				attributes.repeat = paginatedOppurtunities;
				erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", responseText, "");
				erb.setAttributes(attributes);
				erb.setEnd(false);
				result = erb.getResponse();
			}else{
				erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Sorry there are no oppurtunities associated to this account", "");
				erb.setAttributes(attributes);
				erb.setEnd(true);
				result = erb.getResponse();
			}
	}
	
	
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>anil.akula</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-24 22:12:44</sys_created_on><sys_id>c1281b3ddbc6e200c2f3717bbf961940</sys_id><sys_mod_count>25</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>anil.akula</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-26 08:14:10</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="DELETE"><active>true</active><keyword>WHOAMI</keyword><name>Who am I</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	var num = "INC" + content.Number.value;
	
	var inc = new GlideRecord('incident');
	if (inc.get('number', num)){
		var updatedArr = inc.sys_updated_on.getDisplayValue().split(" ");
		var updatedDate = updatedArr[0];
		var updatedTime = updatedArr[1].split(":");
		updatedTime = updatedTime[0] + ":" + updatedTime[1];
		
		var notes = inc.comments.getJournalEntry(-1);
		var na = notes.split("\n\n");
		notes = na[0];
		
		//Message output...
		msg = "<speak>";
		msg += "The current status of your incident is: " + inc.state.getDisplayValue() + ". ";
		msg += "Your incident was last updated on: " + updatedDate + " at " + updatedTime  + ". ";
		
		if (notes != "" && notes != null) {
			notes = notes.split("\n");
			msg += "The last update was: " + notes[1] + ".";
		}
		
		msg += "</speak>";
		erb.setOutputSpeech("SSML", "", msg);
		//End message output
	} else {
		erb.setReprompt("PlainText", "I was unable to find that Incident. What was that Incident number again?");
	}
	erb.setEnd(true);
	
	result = erb.getResponse();
	
	
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>jc</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-04-20 22:35:31</sys_created_on><sys_id>0679b69713f61600d0143d622244b09a</sys_id><sys_mod_count>32</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>chaitanya.s</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-17 08:02:20</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>

				attributes.next = 'ContinueIntent,RepeatIntent';
				responseText = paginatedOppurtunities.join(',');
				responseText += ',you can say .continue.for next set of list,or cancel for new query ';

				paginatedOppurtunities = oppurtunities.slice(attributes.currentIndex,attributes.oppurtunities.length);

		attributes.repeat = paginatedOppurtunities;
		erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", responseText, "");

		result = erb.getResponse();

sys_update_xml.name: x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance_a056a8e4db42a200c2f3717bbf961964
sys_update_xml.payload:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance"><x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><active>true</active><keyword>PriorityIntent</keyword><name>PriorityIntent</name><next/><script><![CDATA[(function(content, attributes, erb){
	if(attributes && attributes.short_description && content.number && content.number.value){
		attributes.urgency = content.number.value;
		// 		gs.info(JSON.stringify(attributes));
		// 		gs.info('instance name'+instanceName);
		// 		gs.info('caller_info'+JSON.stringify(caller_info));
		var alexaUtils = new global.AlexaUtils();
		var incidentNumber = alexaUtils.createIncident(instanceName,token,attributes,caller_info);
		if(incidentNumber){
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Your incident was logged successfully ,here is your incident number "+incidentNumber.split('').join(' '),"");
		}else{
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "I am sorry ,i got confused can you please try after sometime, or else yoy can try one more time by saying my problem is, your problem statment","");
		}
		gs.info('in callerinfo priority'+JSON.stringify(caller_info));
		erb.setAttributes(attributes);
		erb.setEnd(true);
	}else{
		if(!attributes.short_description){
			attributes.next = 'DescriptionIntent';
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "You cant say your urgency before your problem is known , please let me know your problem by saying my problem is .., your problem statement","");
			erb.setAttributes(attributes);
			erb.setEnd(false);
		}else{
			erb.setOutputSpeech("PlainText", "Sorry i missed your urgency level ,can you please rate your level of urgency on a scale of one to three where one is most priority and three is least","");
			erb.setAttributes(attributes);
			erb.setEnd(false);
		}
	}
	result = erb.getResponse();
	
	
})(content, attributes, new EchoResponseBuilder());]]></script><sys_created_by>anil.akula</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2016-09-20 12:01:51</sys_created_on><sys_id>a056a8e4db42a200c2f3717bbf961964</sys_id><sys_mod_count>10</sys_mod_count><sys_updated_by>anil.akula</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2016-09-21 02:54:29</sys_updated_on></x_snc_alexa_snow_utterance></record_update>
